Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這聲音是...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,琉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一樣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那個又要...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,亞莉榭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就算只有你也好 快離開這
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,太遲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你們已經無法從絕望中脫身了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.64,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,顯現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,再次出現在我們面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,災厄降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,謹記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,其乃慘劇之宴
